editorialNotes.standard: Wunderlist is a simple-to-use to-do list app that keeps us on track. Thanks to its recurring items and notifications, we never miss deadlines or forget to grab milk from the store. With collaborative lists that stay in sync across iPhone, iPad, and Mac, we can keep our baseball games, movie nights, and team meetings organized.
